1
00:01:25,700 --> 00:01:29,980
=The Youth Memories=

2
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:32,980
=Episode 30=

3
00:01:43,880 --> 00:01:44,760
Oh, laundry time.

4
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:50,120
You love the braised pork shoulder
with soy sauce of Tianfuhao.

5
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,800
When I passed by Bianyifang Restaurant,

6
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:53,160
I bought some roast duck bone.

7
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:55,000
I'll cook some rice later.

8
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:57,160
Let's have a drink.

9
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:03,480
Is there anything to celebrate?

10
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:07,600
Can't we just have a drink together?

11
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:10,030
By the way,

12
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:11,880
can't you find a way

13
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,480
to help Chunsheng?

14
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:16,760
How do I put it?

15
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,240
Unlikely.

16
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:20,320
Now,

17
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:22,080
the leadership isn't pleased with him.

18
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:23,840
Even if he didn't quit,

19
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,800
he would have a hard time in the future.

20
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:28,640
What about this,

21
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:31,360
let's find him another job,

22
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:32,760
a job suitable for him.

23
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:35,520
Do you remember

24
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:37,600
I didn't agree with him to join
the Anti-smuggling Squad?

25
00:02:38,320 --> 00:02:39,160
Exactly.

26
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:40,760
I must say,

27
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:43,240
honey, I really admire you.

28
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:44,840
You're insightful.

29
00:02:45,720 --> 00:02:46,720
I am

30
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,800
a passionate creature

31
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:50,920
who is loyal to friends.

32
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:53,080
But after these days,

33
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:54,720
I find that

34
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,520
times have really changed.

35
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,320
We're all grown men.

36
00:02:58,600 --> 00:02:59,600
We should act our age

37
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,760
in considering things.

38
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,480
Most of all, I'm

39
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:04,040
more or less a leader now.

40
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,720
I should criticize myself.

41
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,400
In terms of Chunsheng,

42
00:03:07,640 --> 00:03:09,160
I wasn't thoughtful enough.

43
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:11,000
He has a strong personality

44
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:13,160
and isn't good at handling
complex interpersonal relationships.

45
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,480
I even think that he is too immature.

46
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:18,320
I don't mind that he affected me.

47
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,640
The bottom line is...

48
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:21,320
Since when have you started to
hate him?

49
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:25,000
When did you decide to drive him away?

50
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:29,000
No, I...

51
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,400
How could I hate Chunsheng?

52
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:34,560
What do you mean by driving him away?

53
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:35,840
You don't understand

54
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:37,360
why I didn't want you

55
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,520
to work together in the first place.

56
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:39,880
Why?

57
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,840
I was afraid that you would fall out.

58
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:44,600
What are you talking about?

59
00:03:44,640 --> 00:03:45,520
I'm telling you,

60
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:47,560
we're still good friends.

61
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,040
What you're doing now

62
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:51,160
is worse than what I was worried about.

63
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,560
What am I doing?

64
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:00,160
If you can't bear him,

65
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:02,400
you can always ask him to leave.

66
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,000
But sure, you dare not.

67
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:06,280
That would be tantamount to
admitting that you're narrow-minded.

68
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:09,160
You're loyal to your friend and
you can't say it.

69
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,840
So, you played dirty.

70
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,400
What did I play?

71
00:04:21,100 --> 00:04:22,540
(Li Shangyou, General Manager)

72
00:04:23,840 --> 00:04:25,560
A noble man makes friends
with who he chooses.

73
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,200
A base man chooses among
the friends he makes.

74
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,400
Since you insisted on

75
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:29,920
having him work with you
at the beginning,

76
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:31,760
you must accept the consequence.

77
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:34,400
He hasn't changed, but you have.

78
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:36,480
First a noble man, then a base man.

79
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:37,640
You made mistakes again and again.

80
00:04:39,820 --> 00:04:40,340
(Li Shangyou, General Manager)

81
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:43,280
What are you talking about?

82
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,040
I'm a base man?

83
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,040
I helped him

84
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:50,080
when he was frustrated.

85
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,880
I let him join the Anti-smuggling Squad.

86
00:04:52,280 --> 00:04:53,640
I did it for his own good then, and now!

87
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:56,920
For his good?

88
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,920
You colluded with an outsider
to falsely accuse your friend

89
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,000
and you think it's for his own good?

90
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,040
He offended people.

91
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:02,880
What could I do?

92
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:04,520
He is straightforward

93
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:06,000
and he always makes trouble.

94
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,280
Since he joined the squad,

95
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:09,160
I've had to wipe his bottom every day.

96
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:12,480
Now you blame me for his leaving?

97
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:14,880
Do you know what price I paid for him?

98
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,560
You still have a chance
to make it right.

99
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,520
Go to see your good buddy and

100
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:22,520
tell him the dirty tricks you played.

101
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:24,920
I have nothing to say.

102
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:53,360
Chunsheng.

103
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:55,640
Fang, sit down.

104
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:57,400
Did I keep you waiting?

105
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,480
No, I just arrived.

106
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,840
About your work...

107
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:07,640
That's what you asked to see me for?

108
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:13,360
OK, I should sincerely

109
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:14,960
apologize to you.

110
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:17,440
You should scold me.

111
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:19,000
Why would I?

112
00:06:21,520 --> 00:06:22,920
I should have listened to you

113
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:25,240
and not worked with the squad.

114
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,520
If I had listened to you,

115
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:30,800
I wouldn't have implicated Hongjun.

116
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:34,360
What do you mean?

117
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,320
Fang,

118
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:39,800
don't blame Hongjun.

119
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:41,600
He told me about your opinions.

120
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:45,000
We don't hide anything from each other.

121
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:50,160
He didn't blame you.

122
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:51,960
He just couldn't understand.

123
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,800
I didn't understand at first, either.

124
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,360
I thought

125
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:56,720
you seemed to

126
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,440
have a problem with me.

127
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:02,280
But now I understand.

128
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:05,400
You see more and further than us.

129
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,040
Really.

130
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:08,840
People may not know themselves well.

131
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,800
They need to be reminded.

132
00:07:11,320 --> 00:07:11,960
Of course,

133
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,640
not everyone can do this.

134
00:07:14,080 --> 00:07:15,320
Only smart ones can,

135
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:17,040
exceptionally smart ones.

136
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:20,120
I've only met

137
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:22,240
two exceptionally smart people.

138
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:24,840
You are one of them.

139
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:26,600
Who is the other?

140
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,800
My comrade-in-arms,

141
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,200
who died on the battlefield.

142
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:38,320
Speaking of that,

143
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,480
I miss them.

144
00:07:40,280 --> 00:07:41,840
I should make time to visit them.

145
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:48,160
By the way, do you have
anything else to say?

146
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:52,200
Nothing else.

147
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:55,400
I'm worried that you would

148
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:56,400
feel depressed after losing your job.

149
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,760
I want to straighten you out.

150
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,520
Are you making fun of me?

151
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:00,240
No.

152
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:03,040
Alright.

153
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,640
For the sake of your friendship,

154
00:08:05,400 --> 00:08:06,760
I should pull myself together.

155
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:11,480
How is Hongjun doing?

156
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:14,560
He...

157
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,360
is fine.

158
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:21,320
Fang,

159
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:23,680
you should give him some guidance.

160
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:25,480
He listens to you.

161
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:27,400
Tell him

162
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:30,360
to explain himself to his leader

163
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:32,720
and pull himself together.

164
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:35,400
Don't let me affect him.

165
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,400
One more thing,

166
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:42,960
Hongjun has a promising future.

167
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:45,240
As he gets promoted,

168
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:46,840
there will be

169
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,440
more and more temptation.

170
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,120
He is a smart guy.

171
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:54,040
But the smarter a guy is,
the more likely he is to make mistakes

172
00:08:54,520 --> 00:08:55,360
and think highly of himself.

173
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,680
You know him the best.

174
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:00,680
Remind him of that

175
00:09:00,920 --> 00:09:01,760
when you get a chance.

176
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:03,800
OK.

177
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:29,760
You're back, honey.

178
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:37,880
I went to your campus today.

179
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:39,960
Your colleagues told me

180
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,160
you left immediately after class.

181
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:42,680
Where have you been?

182
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:44,920
Chunsheng said that

183
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,760
he should have listened to me
and not bothered you.

184
00:09:48,160 --> 00:09:49,400
Now he got you into trouble.

185
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,120
He felt guilty.

186
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,240
He also said that

187
00:09:53,640 --> 00:09:55,600
you were his good friend and buddy.

188
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:57,080
You never hid anything from each other.

189
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:58,760
You told him everything.

190
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,680
And also, you had a promising future.

191
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,120
Did you see Xiao Chunsheng?

192
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,720
Do you feel ashamed?

193
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:14,160
Did you tell him everything?

194
00:10:15,520 --> 00:10:16,280
Ye Fang,

195
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,720
how could you betray me?

196
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:23,960
Chen Hongjun, how can you
shift the blame to me?

197
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,320
Since you became

198
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:28,000
the president
of the Student Union in college,

199
00:10:28,640 --> 00:10:30,640
you've never admitted any mistakes.

200
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:32,840
You would blame everything on others.

201
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,640
Is that so hard to

202
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,320
admit your mistakes and apologize?

203
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:40,840
Why should I apologize?

204
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:41,840
Why should I?

205
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:43,680
People who get in
using their connections

206
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,080
are all timid at work,

207
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,320
lest make trouble.

208
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,280
What about Xiao Chunsheng?

209
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,720
He stood up for others

210
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:50,160
and put me on the opposite side
of my superior.

211
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:51,680
Has he ever considered me?

212
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,480
Honestly, do you regret it?

213
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:57,800
Ye Fang, I think you regret it.

214
00:10:58,560 --> 00:11:00,440
If you hadn't put on the show
with me in the first place,

215
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,600
you must have had a meteoric rise.

216
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:04,280
Then you needn't bother to

217
00:11:04,400 --> 00:11:06,000
educate me like I'm your son.

218
00:11:29,560 --> 00:11:32,760
(Learning that Ye Fang
had seen Xiao Chunsheng,)

219
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:34,280
(Chen Hongjun was worried.)

220
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:38,000
(He made up an excuse
to visit Xiao Chunsheng.)

221
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:41,840
Hongjun,

222
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:43,680
sit down.

223
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:56,960
(Seeing that he was normal,)

224
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:59,600
(Chen Hongjun felt relieved.)

225
00:12:04,860 --> 00:12:07,620
(Unit One)

226
00:12:10,160 --> 00:12:11,920
If I don't have to prepare for the exam,

227
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,880
I'll go to Yunnan with you.

228
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:16,080
Just focus

229
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,400
on your exam.

230
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:19,000
We can go anytime

231
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,480
when you want to.

232
00:12:21,560 --> 00:12:22,320
OK.

233
00:12:22,760 --> 00:12:23,920
You should enjoy a diversion.

234
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:27,720
I just miss my comrades-in-arms.

235
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,400
I want to see them.

236
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:32,960
Feel free to go.

237
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:34,680
I'll visit Yanqiu and Tian

238
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:37,360
whenever I have time. Don't worry.

239
00:12:40,680 --> 00:12:41,360
Xiaomei,

240
00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:43,320
I'm so lucky to have you.

241
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:54,280
(He Hongling was under)

242
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:56,800
(great pressure in the new band.)

243
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:01,440
(To establish her position
as the concertmaster,)

244
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:04,000
(He Hongling, competitive as always,)

245
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:06,440
(kept practicing
without sleeping or eating.)

246
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:25,880
Hongling.

247
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:31,000
Hongling.

248
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,240
Hongling.

249
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:42,600
What's wrong with you?

250
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:43,840
Don't you know she's pregnant?

251
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:44,840
It's OK.

252
00:13:48,860 --> 00:13:53,300
(In Surgery Silence Operating Room)

253
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:07,760
The patient is bleeding profusely!

254
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:32,000
Don't worry.

255
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:33,880
We'll have another baby.

256
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:08,800
Chief Duan, you have a visitor.

257
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:11,160
Lei.

258
00:15:12,160 --> 00:15:13,000
Chunsheng!

259
00:15:17,520 --> 00:15:18,360
Since when have you

260
00:15:18,920 --> 00:15:20,480
learned surprising attack?

261
00:15:21,160 --> 00:15:23,080
Chief Duan, keep up your appearance.

262
00:15:23,760 --> 00:15:24,680
Sit down.

263
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:27,040
Let me get you some water.

264
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:31,920
Can you tell me

265
00:15:32,400 --> 00:15:34,520
why you didn't inform me
before you came to Yunnan?

266
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,240
I could've picked you up at the station.

267
00:15:36,800 --> 00:15:38,200
We're good friends.

268
00:15:38,240 --> 00:15:39,040
You don't have to bother.

269
00:15:40,040 --> 00:15:40,600
Have some water.

270
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:48,560
After demobilization, it took me
some time to recover from my injuries.

271
00:15:49,240 --> 00:15:50,200
When my leg got well,

272
00:15:50,520 --> 00:15:52,720
since the Organization recognized
my professional ability,

273
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:54,720
they transferred me
to the Criminal Police Unit.

274
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:56,720
We work day and night here.

275
00:15:57,520 --> 00:15:59,200
Our work is more exhausting than yours.

276
00:16:02,280 --> 00:16:02,920
What about you?

277
00:16:03,640 --> 00:16:04,680
How do you get along with Xiaomei?

278
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:06,000
When will you get married?

279
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:07,880
We'll

280
00:16:07,880 --> 00:16:08,680
get married sooner or later.

281
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:10,760
I just want to find the right time

282
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:13,480
to visit her parents
and ask their permission.

283
00:16:16,160 --> 00:16:17,080
In fact,

284
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:18,880
I've always thought that

285
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:20,880
Xiaomei is more suitable for you.

