But now,

305
00:17:10,520 --> 00:17:11,560
for the sake of money,

306
00:17:12,310 --> 00:17:13,520
my former friend

307
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:15,350
smuggled goods under my name.

308
00:17:16,520 --> 00:17:17,520
For the sake of power,

309
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:19,560
my best buddy

310
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:21,520
contrived to set me up

311
00:17:22,310 --> 00:17:24,070
and forced me out of
the Anti-smuggling Squad.

312
00:17:29,240 --> 00:17:30,680
You do understand.

313
00:17:33,120 --> 00:17:34,400
You just don't want to face it.

314
00:17:37,240 --> 00:17:38,120
People

315
00:17:39,760 --> 00:17:40,480
will change.

