The lack of rehabilitation devices

346
00:18:42,280 --> 00:18:43,160
in China has made

347
00:18:43,840 --> 00:18:44,840
many patients

348
00:18:45,280 --> 00:18:46,800
miss the best time for their treatment.

349
00:18:47,320 --> 00:18:48,720
Take my fellow patients

350
00:18:48,760 --> 00:18:50,080
at the rehabilitation center in Beijing
for example,

351
00:18:50,360 --> 00:18:52,000
they're supposed to have the chance

352
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,080
to recover,

353
00:18:53,520 --> 00:18:55,760
but owing to the lack of devices,

354
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:57,760
