Yes.

373
00:19:46,840 --> 00:19:48,560
Xiang Nan has a big business now.

374
00:19:48,800 --> 00:19:51,240
He is a famous jewelry merchant

375
00:19:51,240 --> 00:19:52,280
in Kunming.

376
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:55,720
I'm not surprised

377
00:19:56,040 --> 00:19:57,280
to hear that.

