00:19:58,280 --> 00:20:00,040
Lei, do you remember

379
00:20:00,600 --> 00:20:02,280
he would risk his life

380
00:20:02,560 --> 00:20:03,760
for a stone?

381
00:20:05,560 --> 00:20:06,360
Yeah.

382
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:08,440
He is a man

383
00:20:08,880 --> 00:20:11,000
with vision and courage.

