00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:14,920
He also keeps old friendship in mind.

385
00:20:15,600 --> 00:20:17,760
Do you still keep in touch with him?

386
00:20:18,160 --> 00:20:19,040
Sure.

387
00:20:19,840 --> 00:20:21,880
He has never forgotten that
we saved his life.

388
00:20:22,040 --> 00:20:23,240
