390
00:20:25,080 --> 00:20:26,520
He asked about you many times.

391
00:20:27,120 --> 00:20:28,280
He said he wanted to repay you

392
00:20:28,760 --> 00:20:29,840
when he got a chance.

393
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:31,760
