394
00:20:32,360 --> 00:20:33,880
I just did what a soldier should do.

395
00:20:38,560 --> 00:20:39,400
Chunsheng,

396
00:20:40,560 --> 00:20:41,560
to be honest with you,

397
00:20:41,800 --> 00:20:43,280
Xiang Nan is a good man.

398
00:20:43,800 --> 00:20:45,160
He deserves to be your friend.

399
00:20:46,760 --> 00:20:47,880
I think

400
00:20:48,080 --> 00:20:49,760
since you're here in Yunnan,

