409
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:13,880
Alright.

410
00:21:14,120 --> 00:21:14,960
Suit yourself.

411
00:21:15,080 --> 00:21:16,200
You go look around

412
00:21:16,440 --> 00:21:17,440
this afternoon.

